{"tid":1690692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你話我分化都好 但有時真係好失望好無助","createTime":"2019-11-03T12:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T12:26:10.000Z","uid":26532,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f4dc2081049ca716273db4095605abf5aa46a138","tid":1690692,"uid":26532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"利申 前線撚 <br />\n<br />\n都差唔多5個月 手足比人拉左三千幾個人都至少死左50幾個<br />\n講撚左全民勇武講撚左四個月都仲係得和理非<br />\n<br />\n口號識叫反抗 但你地撚有反抗過 ? 唱過下歌叫過下口號對得住自已就算?<br />\n反抗係咁架咩?  前線比人拉就係到鳩叫放人 你地做過咩實質野幫過場運動?<br />\n<br />\n岩岩有手足比人斬撚左隻耳 現場既人淨係識叫人唔好打<br />\n人地斬撚左隻耳呀 打撚斷佢手手腳腳都好應該掛? 班左膠淨係叫人唔好打 <br />\n香港人係咁撚垃圾既咩?<br />\n<br />\n偽勇武撚又係仆街啦,累撚死真前線仲要拎撚哂D裝去用 唔敢勇武就認撚左佢啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有屋企直播撚,你地連垃圾都不如"},{"pid":"b46586961d26e0e8c85fe6bf913adc6d18077073","tid":1690692,"uid":336581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:00:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B4ZhACnhiFd/?igshid=du741fhc1clm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4ZhACnhiFd%2F%3Figshid%3Ddu741fhc1clm&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQedFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=40bc7022\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4ZhACnhiFd%2F%3Figshid%3Ddu741fhc1clm&h=19bdd314\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4ZhACnhiFd/?igshid=du741fhc1clm</a><br />\n<br />\n尋晚旺角班狗俾人撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fb8f1ebc1610bddedac1c266bfd6ec6219c396","tid":1690692,"uid":76690,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:01:43.000Z","msg":"你做過咩"},{"pid":"9ea72e90ffba4a4ad735ce828f699f144b718c05","tid":1690692,"uid":110761,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"好嬲  聽日繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431aa9fd11df09807ea4f92e9fba95db6b2e8c83","tid":1690692,"uid":60815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply